History: Version 1.06b COPYRIGHT

15/2/93: 1.00-beta

Started version 1.00-beta
Finished working version on 20/2/93, beta testing.
Problem with snake crashing after a few mins.
Added scoring.

To implement:

+ Timer on food eating
+ High score table of users
+ Instructions screen
: Neater game over screen
+ Baudrate checker and trials at low baud rates
: Levels of difficulty:
     : Extra food
     : Less time
     : Faster growing snake
     : Different respective scoring
: Different screen levels & screen patterns
: Pause/continue option?
: More food eaten the faster the snake?

1/3/93:

Fixed bug with new food being positioned on top of snake
Added a simple instruction screen and wrote ReadMe file.
1st version put onto TWoC for trial.

4/3/93:

Tested at 2400 baud on Arcade found to be too unresponsive to
keypresses, altered key detection repeat loop hopefully make
things better.

16/3/93:

chr 219 full block
Changed screen display and key search routines

18/3/93: 1.01-beta

Added FNf=0 bits in case of dropped carrier, added quit delay
implementation. Sent to Arcade

20/3/93:

Username entry and highscore table added.

22/3/93: 1.02

Final releasable version ready.
Sent to TWoC and Arcade.
Tested at 300 baud... fine!

13/4/93: 1.03 Shareware

Made shareware and added unregistered bits
Added games to date

17/4/93: 1.04

Altered Highscore routines and added title page

26/8/93: 1.05

OPEN file bits

4/4/94: 1.06

Compendium version

25/5/94: 1.06b

Minor bug fix, new food routine checks

8/94: 1.06c

Added more checks for dropped carriers to stop crashing

27/9/94: 1.07

Free version with ArcBBS 1.64



